Global Ertapenem API Market Insights
Ertapenem API Market size was valued at USD 0.9 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 1.5 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 7.2% from 2024 to 2030.

Ertapenem API Market Overview
The global Ertapenem API market is projected to reach USD 1.3 billion by 2028, with a CAGR of 4.5% during the forecast period. This growth is driven by the increasing demand for antibiotics for treating severe infections. Ertapenem is a broad-spectrum beta-lactam antibiotic used to treat a range of bacterial infections, including intra-abdominal infections, pneumonia, and urinary tract infections. The market is expanding due to the rising incidences of hospital-acquired infections (HAIs) and the growing geriatric population. Additionally, government initiatives to combat antibiotic resistance are further propelling the market growth.

